\par\pard\plain \tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\sl360\slmult1\qj\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0 When compiled (File > Compile), this project will generate a script in the BBC\loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8217\'92s standard \u8220\'93scene style\u8221\'94 format for radio. Please see the \u8220\'93BBC Radio Format: Scene Style\u8221\'94 specifications for a description of the expected format, which you can find on the BBC Script Smart website here:}
